welcome_message_body: Welcome to Carney, a charming city known for its beautiful parks, friendly community, and rich history. We hope you enjoy your stay and explore all that our lovely city has to offer.

terminals.name: Main Terminal

terminals.description: The private terminal at Glenn L Martin Airport is reserved for private and charter flights, offering a luxurious and exclusive experience for passengers.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
